{
  "stem": "20848.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they cut off my mother from me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They counted 100, like 20 rows, and my mother marched off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And here I was left in the first row, a child on its own, without a father, without a mother, without my brother.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was standing there, and with the other people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "A lot of people knew us because they were working with us and living in Leszno, some people knew us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were terrible, terrible mud there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I lost my shoe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We stayed there for a while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then they started marching us, they count another 100 and started marching.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And a man in a striped suit noticed that I have lost one shoe in the mud.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he ran quickly-- no, he was perhaps 100 meters away, there were barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he ran quickly and threw the shoes at me, a new pair of shoes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I grabbed the shoes and they fitted me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they marched us, and they marched us to a place which later on I found was a sauna.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And before we marched to the sauna, there was one SS-man sitting here and one SS-man sitting there, and he made a selection.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he put all the children and women and old people to one side, and all young women to other side.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Now I remember what my father said, you do the opposite what the Germans tell you to do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And also by that time, I knew that the children and all the people would be gassed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "By the time, we knew, what-- that they were gassing the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- he put me as the first.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "SS-man put me together with the children and the women on this side.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
